      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything is just... gone. i stared at the screen for three hours and i still cant make it make sense. i lost everything. i look in the mirror and i dont even see a person anymore, just a massive mistake. i feel like im just falling into this void and there's no floor. i'm already at the bottom, i might as well just stay here.",
