      "content": "your belief that you do not belong confirms the massive lie that nothing matters, because true existence is defined by the struggle to prove otherwise despite the pain. The relief you feel is not freedom but the dangerous luxury of believing that stopping the fight is a valid escape from a world that never truly gave up on you. We are still here, fighting for another breath, and that simple act of enduring is the only truth left when everything else turns to dust.",
